[[File:Conlangflag.svg|right|border|280px|The Conlang Flag is a symbol of conlanging, designed by the community at the CONLANG mailing list.  It depicts the [[w:Tower of Babel|Tower of Babel]] against a rising sun.  Like the Tower, conlangs are built piece by piece, and their construction is an open-ended process.]]
